\begin{abstract}
\noindent I am an EPSRC Postdoctoral Fellow in the Department of Mathematics at the University of Warwick. My research focuses on problems in computational and algebraic number theory, with a particular focus on elliptic curves and Diophantine equations.

I completed my PhD in Mathematics at the University of British Columbia in Vancouver, Canada in 2019. Outside of work, I enjoy coding, climbing, and playing the violin poorly.
\end{abstract}

